{"tid":2158801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美卿轉抵波蘭　簽署國防合作協議   增兵波蘭  從德國撤軍","createTime":"2020-08-16T02:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T07:01:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f87fd076329d5410f200e3dbc18ea874b55e919d","tid":2158801,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543930-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543930-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a30daa7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543930-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=03ce284f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543930-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧抵達波蘭，展開歐洲四國訪問行程的最後一站，與總理莫拉維茨基會談，討論新型肺炎疫情、5G網絡建設、白俄羅斯局勢、發展能源計劃等議題。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又與波蘭國防部長簽署國防合作協議，為部份駐德國美軍，重新部署到波蘭鋪平道路。根據去年的雙邊決定，美國將會向波蘭增派1000名美軍，令駐當地美軍人數增至5500人。"},{"pid":"e4383a5ad2cc86b8410749627360be3d3a8cefbf","tid":2158801,"uid":243677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"新世界民主聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9612468af2f64ec2b18a551a20007799ddb818f","tid":2158801,"uid":200070,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁又咩分別 德國都係怕俄羅斯 <br />\n而家擺係波蘭咪對德國更加有利"},{"pid":"0c7647f1a55cdd498f7bfeecf03d2c3585bc5830","tid":2158801,"uid":63108,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e9612468af2f64ec2b18a551a20007799ddb818f","tid":2158801,"uid":200070,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"repl